cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.DS, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper discusses link recommendation in social networks and the impact of suggested links on information diffusion. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also uses the Independent Cascade model to model influence diffusion, which falls under cs.SOC (Social and Economics Networks) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also involves optimization to maximize influence, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
